messages.ssml: <speak>According to the Center for Disease Control and Prevention, current symptoms reported for patients with <sub alias="covid 19">COVID-19</sub> have included mild to severe respiratory illness with fever, cough, and difficulty breathing. Symptoms may appear 2-14 days after exposure.</speak>
